% Basic presburger entailment test (BETA spec section 2.3.4).
% A `presburger "phi"` goal succeeds iff phi is entailed by the
% current arithmetic constraints. Outer-scope sharing maps a free
% identifier inside the literal to the LV_Named of the same spelling.
%
% Expected:
%   ?- X is 7, presburger "X > 5".   => yes.
%   ?- X is 3, presburger "X > 5".   => no.
